WEBVTT

00:05.704 --> 00:07.404
Gunshot?

00:07.406 --> 00:08.739
That's no
gunshot wound.

00:08.741 --> 00:09.940
Looks like he
was stabbed.

00:09.942 --> 00:10.974
You get an I.D.?

00:10.976 --> 00:12.743
No, no wallet.

00:12.745 --> 00:14.144
Robbery?

00:14.847 --> 00:15.812
It's a good bet.

00:15.814 --> 00:18.015
His watch is missing.

00:18.017 --> 00:20.783
This isn't exactly
a high traffic area.

00:20.785 --> 00:22.718
Don't think we're gonna
get many eyewitnesses

00:22.720 --> 00:24.020
coming out of
the woodwork.

00:24.022 --> 00:26.889
No, and anything that was
left behind's washed away--

00:26.891 --> 00:29.526
fibers, hairs,
footprints.

00:29.528 --> 00:32.494
If a tree falls in the forest
and no one's around to hear it,

00:32.497 --> 00:34.230
does it make a sound?

00:36.468 --> 00:39.368
It doesn't matter if there's
a camera in the forest.

00:45.643 --> 00:47.276
I gave you ten dollars!

00:47.278 --> 00:48.744
You give me five,
I give you two.

00:48.746 --> 00:49.779
Hot dog is three.

00:49.781 --> 00:50.980
I gave you ten!

00:50.982 --> 00:52.715
You gave me five,
now get lost

00:52.717 --> 00:54.716
before I call the police!

00:56.019 --> 00:57.819
That's enough. Calm down.

00:57.821 --> 00:59.788
That's enough. That's enough.
Whoa, whoa. Hey, hey, hey.

00:59.790 --> 01:01.056
- Hey, hey.
- That's enough. Calm down.

01:01.058 --> 01:02.924
O-Okay. Okay, okay!

01:02.926 --> 01:04.593
Look, look, look,
I got, I got...

01:04.595 --> 01:06.962
I got something in my pocket
that will get me out of this.

01:06.964 --> 01:07.929
Oh, yeah? Like what?

01:07.931 --> 01:09.764
Just check my wallet.

01:11.167 --> 01:13.234
As usual, you missed the point.

01:13.236 --> 01:14.636
You asked my opinion,
I gave it.

01:14.638 --> 01:16.204
And it was wrong.
It's my opinion.

01:16.206 --> 01:17.572
It can be neither
right nor wrong.

01:17.574 --> 01:19.307
It can be wrong and it was.

01:19.309 --> 01:20.675
And you were right, right?

01:20.677 --> 01:22.611
Right.
Where's Baker?

01:22.613 --> 01:23.812
In labor.

01:23.814 --> 01:25.814
Careful, Sid, he hasn't
had his coffee yet.

01:25.816 --> 01:27.482
What is it?

01:27.484 --> 01:28.949
Uh, an individual was
arrested this morning

01:28.951 --> 01:30.784
after he assaulted a hot
dog vendor on the street.

01:30.786 --> 01:33.254
Okay.

01:33.256 --> 01:35.556
In the 12th, Officer
Reagan's precinct.

01:35.558 --> 01:37.091
This going somewhere?

01:37.093 --> 01:39.193
Officer Reagan asked me to
bring it to your attention

01:39.195 --> 01:42.062
that the perp had on him
an NYPD courtesy card.

01:42.064 --> 01:43.530
An old one of mine.

01:43.532 --> 01:46.166
No, an old one
of your son's, Joe.

01:48.000 --> 01:54.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:58.914 --> 02:01.748
Anthony ABETEMARCO!

02:01.750 --> 02:03.583
Hey! Jimmy boy!

02:03.585 --> 02:05.018
How the hell
are you, pal?

02:05.020 --> 02:06.353
How you doing, huh?

02:06.355 --> 02:08.255
Eh, can't complain.

02:08.257 --> 02:09.622
What's new?
What's new?

02:09.625 --> 02:10.889
Yeah.
I'm still fat.

02:10.892 --> 02:12.259
That's the only news I got to report.

02:12.261 --> 02:14.594
Nah, you look good, man.
You look good.

02:14.596 --> 02:16.195
What about you?
Staying out of trouble?

02:16.197 --> 02:17.697
Yeah, nah, you know,
yeah, yeah, yeah.

02:17.699 --> 02:19.132
You still
chasing the action.

02:19.134 --> 02:21.801
Yeah, ooh, well,
you know, big shock, huh?

02:21.803 --> 02:24.303
You up or down?

02:24.305 --> 02:26.673
Ah, I'm down and out, Ant.

02:27.742 --> 02:29.208
How deep are you
in the hole?

02:31.445 --> 02:33.445
Ah, Jimmy, to who?

02:33.447 --> 02:37.616
To this group out
in, uh, Bay Ridge. Russians.

02:37.618 --> 02:39.451
We're not bumping into
each other on accident

02:39.453 --> 02:40.852
out here, are we?

02:40.854 --> 02:42.388
You know, I, uh, heard
you worked around here.

02:42.390 --> 02:44.122
I thought I could
hit you up for a favor.

02:44.124 --> 02:45.591
You want me to sit down
with these guys?

02:45.593 --> 02:47.759
Just flash the badge around,
let 'em know I'm a good guy,

02:47.761 --> 02:48.927
and I'm good for it.

02:48.929 --> 02:50.862
How you gonna be
good for it, Jimmy?

02:50.864 --> 02:52.463
I got it all worked out,
it's all good.

02:52.465 --> 02:54.232
I just... I need more time,
you know?

02:55.069 --> 02:57.069
Let me think about it, okay?

02:57.071 --> 02:58.303
No promises.

02:58.305 --> 03:00.572
Yeah, do what you
got to do, I mean...

03:00.574 --> 03:02.107
It's good to see you.

03:02.109 --> 03:03.341
You, too, buddy.

03:25.131 --> 03:26.130
Hey!

03:26.132 --> 03:29.433
Hey, I got something.

03:29.435 --> 03:30.567
What do you got?

03:30.569 --> 03:32.569
Miracle of all miracles,
the surveillance camera

03:32.571 --> 03:35.572
at the crime scene was
actually in working condition.

03:35.574 --> 03:36.841
Well, let's take a look.

03:39.177 --> 03:41.745
This poor guy has
no idea what's coming.

03:41.747 --> 03:42.779
Here we go.

03:42.781 --> 03:44.715
Your money
or your life.

04:07.472 --> 04:08.772
Now, what the hell
was that?

04:08.774 --> 04:10.907
It's not a straight-out
robbery, that's for sure.

04:10.909 --> 04:13.776
No, it looks more like a hit
made to look like a robbery.

04:25.790 --> 04:29.790
